<div class="ds-eyebrow">Component library</div>
<h1 class="ds-title">Components</h1>
<p class="ds-lede">A new Curie page is an arrangement of existing components on the dark canvas — you compose, you don't invent painted components. Each entry below carries a live preview, its anatomy, and the judgment for when to reach for it.</p>
<div class="ds-example-grid">
{% for c in manifest.components %}
  <a class="ds-component-card" href="/components/{{ c.id }}/">
    <span class="cat">{{ c.category }}</span>
    <h3>{{ c.name }}</h3>
    <p>{{ c.purpose }}</p>
  </a>
{% endfor %}
</div>
